name: Fred Eats a 3D Egg (fea3de)
description:
Fred grows a hand and becomes three dimensional. (i am aware of the typo "dimentional") these games took 3 days to make each. so, dont expect much.

Fred's Funni Bundle is not really a game, but it has 4 of them in one file. These games were made using clickteam 2.5 (FEA3DE is made with Unreal Engine 5.0.3) Not really much into these games but they took a while to make, but they are short. (beat the 3d game and you can see my plans for another game) Basically just do what you can and report any bugs to- somewhere- idk my gmail maybe- (coolfreddyboi@gmail.com) we have free cookies here, and we also sell planes for one dollar. private jets included. make sure you get your wallets out, because the fee to come here is $0.00.
